packages needed on raspbian:

sudo apt-get install libxml2
sudo apt-get install libxml2-dev
sudo apt-get install libcurl3
sudo apt-get install libcurl4-openssl-dev

libbass-hardfp ARM

picotts:

sudo apt-get install libpopt-dev
sudo apt-get install libexpat1-dev

Hardware:

Raspberry Pi A+

speaker - Visaton FRWS 5 R

opamp 
 - NE5532

PSU board for opamp: 
 - LM2577 S ADJ
 - ICL7660
 - solid state relay (P/N?) 

RTC + NVRAM board
 - DS1397
 - Atmel 24C512 DIP8 (64KB)

display:
 - Winstar WEH001602


